OwnerTransactionVerificationController ..> PaymentProof
OwnerTransactionVerificationController ..> Notification

OwnerReportController ..> GeneratedReport
OwnerReportController ..> Transaction
OwnerReportController ..> Expense
OwnerReportController ..> Room

OwnerAdminManagementController ..> User
OwnerAdminManagementController ..> AdminProfile
OwnerAdminManagementController ..> AdminActivityLog

